Ranger Help for: bio
====================

SYNTAX:      bio
             bio <text>
USAGE:       Anywhere.

SUMMARY:
View or set your personal Ranger biography. Your bio is a short
description of your character's background. Without an argument,
shows your current bio. With text, sets a new bio (max 500 chars).

Also accessible as 'myinfo'.

=============================================================================
